@node "todo" "The ToDo-List"
The following ideas would be interesting enough, to be integrated into the
program. Therefore they are standing on my ToDo-list:

- At processing the given path (scanning / replacing default tools) there
  should also the sub-directories be processed, dependend of an user setting.

- A font sensitive window layout.

- If an entry in a list is too long for being displayed in full length,
  it should be right justified, to display the program name correctly.
@endnode
